    "5, mostly containing scanned documents.",
    "Then, in Sect. 6, partially annotated collections are described, focused only on challenging parts of scientific documents such as tables and figures.",
    "Finally, large-scale fully annotated datasets are listed in Sect. 7.",
    "For completeness, in Sect. 8 we provide a broader overview of significant datasets that are related to DLA for different types of documents, and in Sect.",
    "9 we discuss and summarize the impact and complexity of each collection presented in this survey, along with the latest state-of-the-art methods tested on the datasets."
